query:
SELECT 
                rooms.id, 
                rooms.name, 
                JSON_AGG(
                    JSON_BUILD_OBJECT(
                        'id', room_members.player_id,
                        'username', users.username,
                        'owner', room_members.owner
                    )
                ) as players 
                FROM rooms 
                LEFT JOIN room_members ON room_members.room_id = rooms.id 
                LEFT JOIN users ON room_members.player_id = users.id 
                GROUP by rooms.id
